title: Windows: Broadcom Bonding Network Interface
agents: windows
catalog: os/networking
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check checks the current state of a Windows broadcom bonding interface.
 If the total bonding state of the interface is down, then the
 check gets critical. If at least one slave interface is down the check
 gets WARN.

item:
 The name of the bonding interface

discovery:
 One service is created for each {active} bonding interface.
